{"tid":2253152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共修訂<發動戰爭條件>  增列「發展利益」受威脅就可以全國動員","createTime":"2020-10-22T03:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:00:19.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71053eef1e2ff197f3d7c0ba3adf99ee9b55284e","tid":2253152,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://uploadimg2.moore.ren/images/news/2019-04-22/154311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuploadimg2.moore.ren%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F2019-04-22%2F154311.jpg&h=4bdf7572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者陳政錄／綜合報導<br />\n在中美、台海局勢緊張的背景下，中共中央21日公布《中華人民共和國國防法（修訂草案）》，向公眾徵求草案修改意見，並在第八章「國防動員和戰爭狀態」內容中，<span class=\"red\">主動增加了「發展利益」四字，與國家主權、統一、領土完整、安全等要件，一同並列為中共發動戰爭、進行全國動員或部分動員的先決條件。</span><br />\n<br />\n據央視報導，大陸國防法修訂工作正式啟動是在2019年1月。目前，修訂草案已經國務院常務會議和中央軍委常務會議討論通過，草案正於中國人大網公布，徵求意見的時間是在10月21日至11月19日。"},{"pid":"c8f432ede0bf2f74a50775bbfc6bf1b54132501e","tid":2253152,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15e00bcf0f0cdde4c85f5a7f1e940aac72509cf5","tid":2253152,"uid":66378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"向公眾徵求草案修改意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b58c02211d9debf73f397bc01824c57ef134b0","tid":2253152,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"晒氣啦 日日喊打喊殺"},{"pid":"133c7e5d93000c678d1f40a41ffb2324a33b4479","tid":2253152,"uid":299436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"講就凶狠<br />\n落場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJUD7T7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJUD7T7.gif&h=240e0400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"838856abaa721b8072cb09f0f3c05ec11bd1c21d","tid":2253152,"uid":323720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"